name: gmp
raw_recipe:
{% set version = "6.1.0" %}

package:
  name: gmp
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  fn: gmp-{{ version }}.tar.bz2
  url: ftp://ftp.gnu.org/gnu/gmp/gmp-{{ version }}.tar.bz2
  md5: 86ee6e54ebfc4a90b643a65e402c4048

build:

  skip: true  # [win]

requirements:

    - m4

test:

    - test.c

about:

  license: GPL 2 and LGPL 3
  summary: The GNU multiprecision library.

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - asmeurer
    - isuruf
    - jakirkham
